&lt;p&gt;If you are a motivated, enthusiastic and organised individual who enjoys a challenge and a wide variety of work, then this could be the ideal position for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be capable of working on your own, able to use your initiative and work well under pressure. You will be part of the Gynae admin team and so good communication and interpersonal skills are essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 9th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
